{"tid":540770,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]一團火DSE 應試分享會2018（第２場） - 再接再厲","createTime":"2018-01-25T20:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T13:33:08.000Z","uid":114788,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e96d95a9f46789f939564e981d0df8b187f5571c","tid":540770,"uid":114788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T20:03:44.000Z","msg":"仲有唔夠100日就ＤＳＥ啦! 2018dser 你地準備成點？ <br />\n<br />\n一團火義補計劃會喺11/2係城大舉行DSE分享會，由幾位喺DSE攞到佳績嘅過來人分享中、英、數、通識科的應試心得，為各位打打氣，誠邀各位應屆ＤＳＥ考生參加。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅同學可以透過下面條link係google form報名，費用全免㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]莫問前程凶吉　但求落幕無悔<br />\n共勉之！[/size=4]</span></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iny0Fc54Ft0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIny0Fc54Ft0&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bwwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=68854287\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iny0Fc54Ft0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/233905_a1ba27b7775c774d2ae83b210fd0cd29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2F233905_a1ba27b7775c774d2ae83b210fd0cd29.jpg&h=55c20bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【一團火】DSE應試分享會 - 報名表（中學生）: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/j5CKp5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fj5CKp5&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bwwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=972aee2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/j5CKp5</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n                  DSE應試分享會詳情<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n日期：2018年2月11日（星期日）<br />\n時間：10:30-11:25 通識科<br />\n            11:30-12:30 中文科<br />\n            13:30-14:30 英文科<br />\n            14:35-15:30 數學科<br />\n地點：香港城市大學<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n很多基層小朋友渴望得到免費補習的機會，邀請你加入義補導師及同行者的行列，燃起更亮的一團火！你願意出一分力解決香港跨代貧窮問題嗎？<br />\n「一團火」Facebook 專頁︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onfire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fonfire.hk%2F&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bwwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=cfed71e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onfire.hk/</a><br />\n「一團火網誌」︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.onfire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.onfire.hk&d=FMYnpSuaBq0AgGLdAW2bwwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d1972da8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.onfire.hk</a>"},{"pid":"5ad8eed86a547e4bf8ad344fa865753cb1db4793","tid":540770,"uid":114788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0359f2422e5034ca549445b1f7b9a26a21acd2","tid":540770,"uid":137166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3d55c00d0056705899f3c7556da73e1600362ed","tid":540770,"uid":161352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"搞應試講座不如搞oral"},{"pid":"1f09e29b9a9e469b8a0c605278ee9d1fc2d43d34","tid":540770,"uid":114788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3d55c00d0056705899f3c7556da73e1600362ed","tid":540770,"uid":161352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"搞應試講座不如搞oral"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"呢個方向可以諗下...<br />\nThx for your opinion...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b4b06c55cc0f606a5518d0261e3596b065be03","tid":540770,"uid":114788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f0359f2422e5034ca549445b1f7b9a26a21acd2","tid":540770,"uid":137166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"